project: handsontable
vertion: 0.10.0
issue: https://github.com/handsontable/handsontable/issues/1366
desc: the original value of the cell is lost after entering an invalid value in a dropdown field

steps: click color dropdown component -> set value green -> reclick the dropdown -> input an invalid value
expected: the dropdown value should be the most recent value.
result: the dropdown value is the first value in the list.



